    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-07-09T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-07-09T00:00:00-05:00" n="370" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d370">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Adee</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Taylor</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-07-09">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 9,
                                1895</hi>.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your 377, June 20, not received in time for instructions respecting
                            proposed July 5 interview. You will report by cable the substance of
                            what took place. You will limit your action for the present to
                            instructions already given.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Adee.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
